	<div style="position: relative; top: 6px; left:5px; font-weight: bold; font-size: 13px; padding-left: 45px;">Dynamic signature and Avatar</div>	
	<div style="position: relative; top: 6px; left:10px;">
<img src="http://www.magelocdn.com/images/website/shared/right_menu/support_icone_off.png?v=12010" height="15" style="position: absolute; top:0px; left:0px;" width="33" class="png32" /><img src="http://www.magelocdn.com/images/website/localized/right_menu/eq_discover_icone.png?v=12010" height="24" style="position: absolute;top:-13px; left:7px;" width="24" class="png32" />	</div>
	<hr class="line">
	<br>
For each character you add on Magelo, you will get an avatar and a signature in 2 different sizes with dynamic data that stay up-to date wherever you post them. 
Use them to establish your online identity in your favorite forum! They will give others a quick preview of your character and link its profile.
<br><br>
<img src="http://www.magelocdn.com/images/eq/faq/eq_sig_avatar.png?v=12010" height="" alt="" width="" class="png32" />
<br><br>The signature exists in 2 sizes, a regular sig for any character you want to highlight, and a mini-sig that is really convenient to let others preview your many alternate characters. Combine them the way you want in your posts!
<br>&gt Signature content: Name, level, race, class, server, guild info, up to 6 stats.
<br>&gt Avatar content: Class background and level. 
<br><br>
Premium member can customize their signatures and avatar with background image, font style and color, color theme and cool frames! 

	<div class="CLEANER">&nbsp;</div>
<br>					
	<div style="position: relative; top: 6px; left:5px; font-weight: bold; font-size: 13px; padding-left: 45px;">Game database</div>	
	<div style="position: relative; top: 6px; left:10px;">
<img src="http://www.magelocdn.com/images/website/shared/right_menu/support_icone_off.png?v=12010" height="15" style="position: absolute; top:0px; left:0px;" width="33" class="png32" /><img src="http://www.magelocdn.com/images/website/localized/right_menu/eq_discover_icone.png?v=12010" height="24" style="position: absolute;top:-13px; left:7px;" width="24" class="png32" />	</div>
	<hr class="line">
	<br>
<div style="position: relative; float: left; width: 440px;">
	Knowledge is power. This is particularly true when it comes to MMOGs where there are literally thousands of quests, weapons, armors, creatures or zones to discover. 
	Explore our game database designed to provide comprehensive information to give you a clear edge in your favorite game.
	<br><br>
	Discover the power of our client <a href="magelo_sync.jspa">Magelo Sync</a> : When you are playing, in real time, Magelo Sync provides information that are directly related to your character in the game!
	You can use those contextual information as shortcuts to our website to find details about the zone where you are and your actual target. 
	<br><br>
	Premium member can use the Item advanced search to search for items based on variables such as name, location (In the inventory for example), the usual tags (Lore, Magic, No Trade, Temporary, etc), slot, Skill%, +DMG Skills, and stat attributes.

</div>

<div style="position: relative; float: left; top: 10px; left: 30px;" >
<img src="http://www.magelocdn.com/images/website/localized/discover_magelo/eq_database.png?v=12010" height="208" style="position: absolute; top: -10px; left: 0px;" alt="" width="312" class="png32" /></div>
	
	<div class="CLEANER">&nbsp;</div>
<br>					
	<div style="position: relative; top: 6px; left:5px; font-weight: bold; font-size: 13px; padding-left: 45px;">Guild tools</div>	
	<div style="position: relative; top: 6px; left:10px;">
<img src="http://www.magelocdn.com/images/website/shared/right_menu/support_icone_off.png?v=12010" height="15" style="position: absolute; top:0px; left:0px;" width="33" class="png32" /><img src="http://www.magelocdn.com/images/website/localized/right_menu/eq_discover_icone.png?v=12010" height="24" style="position: absolute;top:-13px; left:7px;" width="24" class="png32" />	</div>
	<hr class="line">
	<br>
<div style="position: relative; float: left; width: 440px;">

As we know how much important a guild is and how much tedious it can be to manage it, our guild tools aims to facilitate out of the game networking amongst guild members and to provide easy management tools. Discover the main features of our Guild tools :  
   <br><br>In "My guild" section, browse your guild roster, access guild reports as well as managing the guild itself: members, permissions, ranks and recruitment. 
    <br> Plug Magelo's guild roster capabilities to your guild's website, using our export service!
    <br><br> In "Guilds" section, find a guild easily in our database and view all guilds which are currently recruiting.
	<br><br> If you are looking for a guild, create your own announce when you manage your character. It will be visible in your profile. You can also find all guilds which are looking for character profiles like yours.
</div>

